proposal, while saying that it will be fun too, as maybe you can see the university from up close. She smiles a bit as she gets closer to you, her face quite close to yours in an obvious attempt to get you nervous. <i>“You can say that I’m homeschooling you too. How’s about that for your curriculim? So… do you agree to my terms or we should start hostilities just like the old days?.”</i> You think that she has something stuck up her ass, but you take it as an opportunity to understand more of the place and to have an excuse to talk with Celia and see if you can remove it from inside her. You accept her terms, something that pleases her. <i>“Then it’s settled. I’ll look forward to see how this sorts out, “my liege”. ”</i> And with that, you tell her that you must get ready for attending that, so you retire from the place, leaving her walking through the trees as you retire from there.";
			option0Name.text = "Draw the line";
			option1Name.text = "Challenge her";
