		///////////////////////////// confirmationControl 1 - Draw the line // confront her

		if (selector == 0 && confirmationControl == 1) {
			Board.text = "You tell her that despite what she could think, you’re won’t stand being treated like a puppet in some kind of game that she could be playing not only with you, but with the other noblemans as well. You’re your own master and you only wanted for her to know about that so that is settled from the start. Maybe you can play along to get things smooth, but you won’t stand any direct attack to your authority. You’re used to being talked in a common way, but that’s all. You can see that she is even more interested in you after you said that. <i>“My, my, my… The puppy has teeth. ”</i> She closes her eyes for a second, a smile appears in her face as she shrugs. <i>“Of course. I won’t hurt your precious little feelings. You’re one of the firsts persons that say that in my face. So, I’ll pull my punches but I expect you to fight back at least. If not, then where is the fun in that?”</i> She says before opening her eyes once more.\n\nAnd with that, you tell her that you must get ready for attending that, so you retire from the place, leaving her walking through the trees as you retire from there.\n";
