		if (selector == 1 && confirmationControl == 1) {
			Board.text = "You tell her that you want to make her sure that you will make sure that she won’t beat you in the social sense of the word. That even when she thinks that she is acid, that you’ll be even worse than that. You say with a smile that you’re not scared of her, on the contrary, you think that you finally found someone that maybe and just maybe, could probe to be a challenge to you. You like challenged and that she probably thinks the same. <i>“You? A challenge? Don’t make me laugh. I’ve had people more skilled than you for breakfast. I don’t know from where you got those reckless courage, but be sure that it won’t last long with me. I will enjoy when you finally found yourself in your proper place.”</i> You can see that she lost a bit of her composure right there in front of you, and that’s all what you wanted. You smile back at her and nod at her answer.\n\nAnd with that, you tell her that you must get ready for attending that, so you retire from the place, leaving her walking through the trees as you retire from there.";
