			Board.text = "You walk beside her and see that the campus is still calm even when you know that there will be a small group of people outside the office soon enough. You tell her that you can’t allow them to overcome her authority. She has been the Dean of that university for a long time, and that both of you know that there is no one better to work as it. Maybe its time to show them that the old ways of the Citadel and the prissy traditions of the city are best left behind everything. She has your support in this, as you know what the city needs right now and that’s more anarchy and freedom among the people. She is quite surprised from your remarks on the subject. <i>“Do you think so? It would be hard to put these kind of ideas into work, but… I think I like that idea.”</i> ";

