			if (NPCCharList.CharFollower [iCelia].corruptionStage > 0) {
				Board.text = "She takes a second to think about what you said, as her face distorts into the one that you knew from her start. <i>“I think you’re right. Those good-for-nothing won’t tell me what I should or not do with the university. They think high because they are still thinking with the old traditions of the city. They don’t understand progress and they want to halt the evolution of the university right in front of my eyes. And I won’t allow that”</i> You smile at her fiery explosion, as you tell her that she has all your support on that crusade, as you said before. <i>“Hey, that’s amazing. With your support, I’m pretty sure that we’ll be able to reach higher than all on our own. I was wrong with you, you know that? You have your head well placed between your shoulders. ”</i> And you answer by exaggerating the fact that she is saying something good from him. <i>“Don’t force it too much. This is an special occasion.”</i> She jokes a bit.\n\nAfter a couple of minutes of planning about what are you going to do, you leave her to get ready for whatever is about to happen. You leave to your castle to get ready for anyone who has enough courage to go with you. ";
			} else {
